------the_system-entry------
-----the_system-the_interface------

“It is time for each Person to have the Interface that fits his/her needs,  his/her ways of thinking and working best.”

<font class="f-l">F</font>rom all possible information data presentation formats available:<br/>Simple lists<br/>Aggregated lists: by words/tags, by people, by format...<br/>Configuration Blocks: New items block, Hot list1 blocks, Theme block, Alert block, Community block, Experts block...<br/>2D Visual representations: Information Analysis Spectrograph (input, relevancy, time-lines...)<br/>3D Visual representations: 3D Clusters by words/tags, by people, by format<font class="br_f-l">Y</font>ou can create a set of custom interfaces, with the option of giving each Person the possibility to make his/her own specific custom interface, tailored to his/her needs.<br/><br/><font class="br_f-l">A</font>nd, all modern interface types are available:<br/>Web interface: Web application, Website, Intranet, Extra-net, Portal...<br/>Mobile (application) Interface<br/>Desktop interface<div class='read_more'><a href='/a/aisca/read/the_technology-entry'></a></div>

